th: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" />The piece of land, which is currently zoned for agricultural use, offers a long-term development opportunity, Galetti said. “At 111 hectares, this site would be ideally suited for industrial uses such as solar/wind farms or large warehousing park.” “Alternatively, considering the existing hotel and casino on the adjacent property the land could be developed into a theme park, shopping centre or holiday resort come golf course.” <img class="aligncenter wp-image-439275" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Carousel-headline.png" alt="" width="900" height="605" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Carousel-headline.png 640w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Carousel-headline-300x202.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /> <img class="size-full wp-image-439285 aligncenter" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Sun-International-2.png" alt="" width="796" height="644" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Sun-International-2.png 796w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Sun-International-2-300x243.png 300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Sun-International-2-768x621.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> Read: Thousands of jobs on the line at Sun City and other popular hotels and casinos in South Africa